My expertise fields are Squarespace website design, website redesign, custom coding, error fixing, & On-Page SEO. So, why late? Get in touch today for a free consultation on Zoom meeting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I See Previous Work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, Of course. Please give me a message on Fiverr. I will show you some of my best Squarespace website portfolios. I hope you must be happy & love this site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide me on-going maintenance service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, of course. Just need to discuss the project details first & then come to an agreement.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I Transfer from Another Platform?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can migrate your content from various platforms to Squarespace seamlessly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide unlimited revision?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide unlimited revisions until your 100% satisfaction.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why Should I Redesign my Squarespace Site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Enhancing your existing Squarespace site's look and functionality for better user experience and improved online presence. A redesign can modernize aesthetics, optimize for mobile, and boost SEO, attracting more visitors and potential clients.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why Choose Squarespace?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Squarespace offers sleek templates and built-in SEO features, boosting your site's visibility.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I Update the Site Myself?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! Squarespace is user-friendly. I'll provide tips so you can easily manage your content.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What About Domain and Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You need your domain and Squarespace plan. I can guide you through the setup process.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need from me to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
What do you need from me to get started?

This information I needed to get started:
 Info-1: Squarespace login access
 Info-2: Website content details (texts/images/video/logo)
 Info-3: Example website link for the design idea
 Info-4: Website color concept & typography

That's it :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is SEO Included?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Basic on-page SEO is part of my design process. For comprehensive SEO services, check out extras.  I optimize content, headings, meta tags, and images for better search engine rankings.

I hired this guy to redesign our site, he missed his deadline with majority of work untouched, then his work was absolutely armature, Keep telling me he is working hard, he spent more time to message me instead of working on my site, he refunded me but just wasted a week of my time and put me behind in my project
Shohag was excellent to work with and optimized and completely reworked my site. The attention to detail far surpassed my expectations and I definitely recommend his work.

Shohag I. did an INCREDIBLE job on my website, going above and beyond with exceptional attention to detail and true professionalism. His proactive communication and quick responsiveness made the entire process seamless. Highly recommend working with him!
